text: Richard Genserowski (4 July 1875 - 31 December 1955) was a German gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1875 births Category:1955 deaths Category:German male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Germany Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts from Berlin
